org.sql: SELECT attachments.* FROM attachments LEFT JOIN documents ON attachments.container_type = 'Document' AND documents.id = attachments.container_id LEFT JOIN projects ON documents.project_id = projects.id WHERE attachments.author_id = 4 AND projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'documents') IS NOT NULL AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (4, 12)) ORDER BY attachments.id DESC LIMIT 1
